# Documentation: source-direct extraction from upstream
# encode/uvicorn uvicorn/main.py + uvicorn/config.py
# (Python **Click** library; NOT argparse, NOT typer):
#   uvicorn/main.py line 14 (`import click`)
#   uvicorn/main.py lines 34-36 (LEVEL_CHOICES /
#     LIFESPAN_CHOICES / INTERFACE_CHOICES via
#     `click.Choice(list(LOG_LEVELS.keys()))`)
#   uvicorn/main.py line 62 (`@click.command(context_settings
#     ={"auto_envvar_prefix": "UVICORN"})` — AUTO-ENV-VAR-
